<paragraph role="heading" id="hd_id3149785" xml-lang="en-US" level="1" l10n="U"><link href="text/scalc/01/05060000.xhp" name="Merge Cells">Merge Cells</link></paragraph>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151246" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="CHG"><ahelp hid=".">Combines the selected cells into a single cell or splits merged cells.</ahelp></paragraph>
</section>
<section id="howtoget">
<embed href="text/scalc/00/00000405.xhp#fozelzus"/>
</section>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148552" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U">The merged cell receives the name of the first cell of the original cell range. Merged cells cannot be merged a second time with other cells. The range must form a rectangle, multiple selection is not supported.</paragraph>
<paragraph role="note" id="par_id3149665" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U">If the cells to be merged have any contents, a security dialog is shown.</paragraph>
